#: src-en/data/events_sector_hive.xml.append:5
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_hive.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOMB_FLAK_TRANSPORT_DESTROYED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You've succesfully destroyed the transport. Unfortunately, none of the Bomb "
"Flaks survived the battle. Disappointing, but at least you can still scrap "
"the remains of the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_hive.xml.append:10
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_hive.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOMB_FLAK_TRANSPORT_CAPTURE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"No more life-signs detected on the transport. You and your crew open the "
"cargo bay, and inside, you find the Bomb Flaks. A particularly large Bomb "
"Flak catches your attention. This must be the Bomb Flak Mark IV they were "
"talking about! You and your crew carry it back to your ship, and then scrap "
"the exterior."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_hive.xml.append:16
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_hive.xml.append$//event[@name=\"MANTIS_BOMB_FLAK_TRANSPORT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You notice a Mantis Transport nearby, emitting a system-wide hail. \"Selling"
" Bomb Flaks! Mark I, Mark II, Mark III, and even new Mark IV! Great killing "
"annoying systems on Federation ships!\" Considering their message, it's "
"unlikely they'll be willing to sell to you, but maybe you'll get lucky?"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_hive.xml.append:19
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_hive.xml.append$//event[@name=\"MANTIS_BOMB_FLAK_TRANSPORT\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Ask if you can buy a Bomb Flak."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_hive.xml.append:23
